                                                        <p class="text-justify">I, Dr. Malladi Srinivas Reddy, Professor & Principal of Vaageswari College of Pharmacy having 16 years of teaching and 2 years of research experience with 30 publications in national, international journals, published a book and received 2 seminar grants from SERB. Education at Vaageswari College of Pharmacy develops a global outlook and perspective among the students while maintaining standards for their profession. I think that students must be quality enough and additional skills to meet the ever changing needs of the industry. We offer an array of opportunities for all our students to achieve excellence in academic, creative, social, cultural, sporting and ethical endeavors. We encourage students to attend workshops and conferences for the purpose of the interaction with eminent professionals to expose the current scenario of pharmacy education and industrial training. We provide students with a conducive environment which nurtures and inspires the students to be achievers in life. Our institution is having professional memberships in organizations like; TASK, SWAYAM, MOOCs for the purpose to increase innovative skills and knowledge. </p>
                                                        <h5>“Educating the mind without educating the heart is no education at all.”<br>“Education without values, as useful as it is, seems rather to make man a more clever devil” </h5>
